text: “eya allah vetin pæmina tibiyadit, israil daruvan aturin saksikaruvaku eyata samana deyak mata saksida dara, pasu va ohu visvasa kara sitiya di numbala eya pratiksepa kota udagu vuye nam (e gæna) numbala kumak sitannehuda? niyata vasayenma allah aparadhakari janayata maga penvanne næta.” yæyi (nabivaraya) numba pavasanu
